{
    "chapter": 68,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "68:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>{努奈}，此类经文，在《黄牛》章的开始，已做了论述。真主以笔盟誓，以人们用笔所书写的盟誓。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "68:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你凭着真主赐予你的使命，不是一个疯子，你并非是以物配主者所诽谤的疯子。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "68:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你将因肩负使命、不断遭受的困苦而享有不断的赏赐，</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "68:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你确是具有《古兰经》带来的崇高品质，你有最完美的状态，</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "68:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你将看到，这些否认使者的人也将看到，</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "68:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当真理昭示，明了谁才是疯子呢？</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "68:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你的主知道谁偏离了祂的正道，知道谁遵循正道，知道谁迷误于正道，你确是遵循正道的。</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "68:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你不要顺从否认你带来的教诲之人，</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "68:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们觊觎，如果你能以宗教为代价温柔亲切地对待他们，那么他们也会温柔与亲切地对待你，</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "68:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你不要顺从每个常以妄言而盟誓的、卑贱的、</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "68:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>诽谤他人的、在人间搬弄是非制造分歧的、</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "68:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>吝啬于行善的、侵犯他人钱财和身体及生命的、作恶多端的、</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "68:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>粗暴的、陷自己的宗族为不义之人，</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "68:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这是因为他是拥有财产和子嗣的，故他傲慢于信仰真主及其使者，</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "68:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当有人向他宣读我的迹象时，他说：“这只是古人的传说而以。”</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "68:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我将在其鼻子标注上永远抹之不去的耻辱的标记。</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "68:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我以干旱和饥饿考验这些以物配主者，如同我曾考验园圃的主人一样，当时他们发誓要在任何一个穷人未能食其之前的一大早，迅速地收获园圃的果实，</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "68:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>在他们的誓言中没有说 ‘如真主意欲’，</h2>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "68:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>故真主派遣了火，在他们睡觉的时候烧毁了园圃，他们不能灭火保护园圃，</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "68:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>园圃顷刻变成黑色，就像漆黑的夜一样，</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "68:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>早晨，他们彼此呼唤，</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "68:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们说：“如果你们要收获果实，在穷人来前赶紧去你们的园圃吧！”</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "68:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们迅速来到园圃，并窃窃私语，</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "68:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们彼此低声说：“今日绝不让任何一个穷人进入园圃。”</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "68:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们一早就启程，以为自己是可以遏制的，</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "68:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当他们目睹园圃已被烧毁时，他们相互说：“我们确已迷失了我们的道路，</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "68:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>不然！我们被阻止收获园圃的果实，因为我们曾阻止穷人收获园圃果实。”</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "68:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们中最优秀的人说：“难道我没有告诉你们，当你们决意禁止穷人享受园圃时，你们怎不赞美真主、向祂忏悔呢？”</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "68:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们说：“赞美我们的主超绝！我们确因曾决意阻止穷人享受我们园圃的果实而自欺。”</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "68:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>于是他们相互走来彼此嗔怪彼此说的话，</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "68:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们后悔地说：“我们真亏折啊！我们阻止穷人享有他们的权力，我们确是过分的人。</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "68:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>但愿我们的主以更优美的园圃补偿我们，我们只向真主恳求，祈求祂的饶恕，请求祂的赐予。”</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "68:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我就是以这样禁止其享受给养的刑法，惩罚悖逆我的人，后世的惩罚更重大，但愿他们知道惩罚的严厉和长久。</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "68:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>遵循真主命令远离其禁戒的敬畏者，在真主那里他们享有很多乐园，他们于其中享受永不间断的恩典。</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "68:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道，就像麦加的以物配主者所佯称那样，我使顺从者和悖逆者的报酬一样吗？</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "68:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以物配主者们啊！你们怎能以这个不公正的、歪曲的判断来判决呢？</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "68:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道你们有一部供你们诵读的经典，其中说顺从者和悖逆者等同吗？</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "68:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在那部经典里，有你们随意为你们后世的选择？</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "68:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道我与你们之间有以信仰确立的盟约，其规定是你们可以为自己判决吗？</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "68:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你询问说这样话的人们，他们谁为此担保呢？</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "68:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道他们有舍真主以外的匹配，将他们和信士的报酬等同吗？如果他们所称那些匹配使他们和信士报酬等同是诚实的，那让他们唤来那些匹配。</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "68:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>复活日，大难来临，我们的主将揭示每一个人，人们被召唤叩首，信士们叩首，不信道者和伪信者则无法叩首，</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "68:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们的眼睛是卑微的，他们低贱和懊悔，在今世，他们健康的时候，曾被要求向真主叩头，</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "68:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！让我惩罚否认降示于你的这《古兰经》的人吧！我在他们不知觉中一步一步将他们驱赶至惩罚，那是对他们的计策和诱惑。</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "68:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我对他们延缓一段时间，以便他们沉溺于罪恶中，我对不信道者和否认使者的人的计策是周全的，他们不能逃脱，也不能从我的惩罚中得以保全。</p>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "68:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你因号召他们归信而向他们索取酬劳故他们因此而负担太重，并反对你吗？事实恰恰相反，你未向他们索取酬劳，那他们为什么不跟随你呢？</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "68:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>还是他们有幽玄的信息，故他们记录对自己有利的、与你辩论的证据呢？</p>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
                "68:48": {
                    "id": 48
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当坚忍你的主以延缓时间诱惑他们的判决，不要像鱼腹中的厌烦自己的族人-尤努斯（愿主赐其平安）一样，当时，在海里和鱼腹的黑暗中他悲哀祈祷他的主，</p>"
        },
        "49": {
            "verses": {
                "68:49": {
                    "id": 49
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>假若不是真主的怜悯到达他，他必受责难的被鱼抛于荒凉之地，</p>"
        },
        "50": {
            "verses": {
                "68:50": {
                    "id": 50
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他的主选择了他，使他入清廉奴仆之列，</p>"
        },
        "51": {
            "verses": {
                "68:51": {
                    "id": 51
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>不信真主、否认其使者的人，几乎以他们对你愤怒的目光使你跌到，当他们听到降于你的这《古兰经》，他们追随自己的私欲、拒绝真理的说：“带来教诲的使者确是一个疯子。”</p>"
        },
        "52": {
            "verses": {
                "68:52": {
                    "id": 52
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>降示给你的《古兰经》只是对人类和精灵的告诫和警示。</p>"
        }
    }
}